w.miamiherald.com/news/politics-government/voters-guide/article240300096.html|title=Want to vote on whether Trump stays? First come the primaries. Here\u2019s what to know|author=Michelle Marchante|date=February 15, 2020|accessdate=February 15, 2020|work=[[Miami Herald]]}}</ref><section begin=\"FLresults\" />\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:right;\"\n|+ style=\"background-color:#f2f2f2;margin-bottom:-1px;border:1px solid #aaa;padding:0.2em 0.4em\" |2020 Florida Republican primary<ref name=\"FLDOE\">{{Cite web|url=https://results.elections.myflorida.com/downloadresults.asp?ElectionDate=3/17/2020&DATAMODE=|title=March 17, 2020 Primary Election|last=|first=|date=March 31, 2020|website=Florida Department of State|publisher=Florida Division of Elections|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=April 8, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Florida Republican Delegation 2020|url=https://www.thegreenpapers.com/P20/FL-R|publisher=The Green Papers|accessdate=March 11, 2020}}</ref>\n! style=\"text-align:left;\" | Candidate\n! style=\"text-align:center;\" | Votes\n! style=\"text-align:center;\" | %\n! Estimated<br>delegates\n|-{{party shading/Republican}}\n| '''{{sortname|Donald|Trump}}'''\n| '''1,162,984'''\n| '''93.79'''\n| '''122'''\n|-\n| {{sortname|Bill|Weld}}\n|39,319\n|3.17\n|\n|-\n| {{sortname|Joe|Walsh|Joe Walsh (American politician)}} <small>(withdrawn)</small>\n| 25,464\n| 2.05\n| \n|-\n| {{sortname|Rocky De La|Fuente}}\n| 12,172\n| 0.98\n|\n|-\n! style=\"text-align:right;\" | Total\n! 1,239,939\n! 100%\n! 122\n|}<section end=\"FLresults\" />\n\n=== Results by county ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable mw-collapsible mw-collapsed\"\n|+\n! colspan=\"10\" |<small>2020 Florida Republican primary</small>\n<small>(results per county)<ref name=\"FLDOE\" /></small>\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" |<small>County</small>\n! colspan=\"2\" |<small>Donald Trump</small>\n! colspan=\"2\" |<small>Bill Weld</small>\n! colspan=\"2\" |<small>Joe Walsh</small>\n! c